text: The UTSA Roadrunners football program represents University of Texas at San Antonio in the sport of American football. The Roadrunners compete in the Football Bowl Subdivision of the National Collegiate Athletic Association and the West Division of Conference USA. They are coached by Jeff Traylor, who started in 2020.
